/**
 * Minimal robotic voice filter. Zero feedback loops, zero comb filters.
 *
 * Chain: input → highshelf boost → lowshelf cut → waveshaper → peaking EQ → limiter → destination
 *
 * The "robot" character comes from:
 *   - Presence boost at 2kHz (peaking EQ) for that processed-through-speaker sound
 *   - Low cut below 200Hz to remove warm body, leaving just the mid-range
 *   - Gentle waveshaper distortion for digital edge
 *
 * No comb, no delay, no feedback — guaranteed stable, guaranteed no ringing.
 */

